The '''Y'taa''' was a group that petitioned the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], just prior to the [[Black Fleet Crisis]]. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Tolik Yar]] contacted [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], claiming that a problem with the Y'taa petition required her attention; however, it was simply a ruse to get her to approach the [[Senate Hall]], where Yar had installed a [[holosign]] proclaiming "882 DAYS WITHOUT A SHOT FIRED IN ANGER Remember, Peace Is No Accident."

==Behind the scenes==
[[Michael P. Kube-McDowell]] created the Y'taa for his novel, ''[[Before the Storm]]'', published by [[Bantam Spectra]] in [[1996]]. It is not clear if the Y'taa is a [[Species/Legends|species]], a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] or an organization.

